div.p:
WHEN Changes and Loſſes are come on our Eſtates; We ſhall then wiſh;
Oh! That while my Talents were yet in my hands; I had more improv'd them for the Honour & Service of GOD, and honoured the LORD, and Succoured His People, with my Subſtance!
                Then, Sirs, Do this before the Changes come upon you.
